        public GeoCoordinate getRouteGeoCoordinate()
        Returns the Geo-location of the location for use in calculation of a route to the location. Usually the same as value as returned by Result.Location.getGeoCoordinate(), but it's possible coordinate is not accessible from the road. In such case, null is returned.
